llegg til div. nummer av Adresseavisen."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "pluss|kultur"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "ef46d3f503f4c866d2ea012ebd7bc748303b0aa5a65c92bfeb0971c4f9b29846"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-01-19T11:29:06.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Katolikkene fikk ny kirke p\u00e5 en sentral tomt i byen, og det spredte seg en frykt for statskirkens fremtid i Trondheim."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/kultur/article12041573.ece/n7b0ph/ALTERNATES/w980-default/1902%20Katolske%20kirke.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/315ca148eaa2f0fed01d3ae1c9e382598f5cdc1a.jpg?5932c9ed"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Fra damplokomotiv til \u00abkatholsk propaganda\u00bb -adressa.no", "Var redd for \u00abmissioner iblant os\u00bb", "Adresseavisen meget betenkt", "Paven ble \u00abgodt stoff\u00bb"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "315ca148eaa2f0fed01d3ae1c9e382598f5cdc1a"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": "Adresseavisen 250"}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Adresseavisen 250"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["pluss", "kultur"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "religion-and-spirituality"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["katolske menigheten", "kirke", "katolsk", "katolsk kirke"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["st. olavs", "nidarosdomen", "st. elisabeth", "abelsborg", "riesterers", "trondhjemske samlinger 1983", "h\u00f8itomt", "bratt\u00f8ra", "pionerene", "kalvskinnet", "jesu hjerte", "st\u00f8ren", "paven", "riestererer", "domkirken", "gamle scene 200", "adresseavisen", "mer\u00e5kerbanen"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["trondheim", "ila"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["johan chr", "gustav bj\u00